        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">2. Permitted Personal Use</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          You are granted a non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to access and use our interactive calculators (Buy, Borrow, Die; Side-Hustle Tax Predictor; and Debt payoff planner) strictly for personal, non-commercial, and educational evaluation. 
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          You agree not to scrape, reverse engineer, copy, or redistribute the source code, algorithms, logic, or formulas underlying our client-side modules without explicit written consent from the administrators of TaxDebtWealthSuite.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 3 -->
      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">3. Disclaimer of Warranties & Estimates</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          The calculations, outcomes, reports, and tax assessments generated by TaxDebtWealthSuite are mathematical approximations based on user-supplied variables and standard legislative formulas. They are provided on an <strong>"as-is" and "as-available" basis</strong>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed text-amber-300">
          <strong>CRITICAL:</strong> TaxDebtWealthSuite makes no warranties, expressed or implied, regarding the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of tax brackets, national insurance estimates, blended APR timelines, or SBLOC liquidation margins. Tax codes and interest rates change frequently. You should never make capital structures, debt repayment decisions, or leveraged borrowing decisions based solely on these tools. Consult a qualified professional advisor.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 4 -->
      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">4. Limitation of Liability and Hold Harmless</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          In no event shall TaxDebtWealthSuite, its authors, developers, or affiliates be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising out of the use or inability to use the mathematical calculators.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          By using this site, you expressly agree to hold TaxDebtWealthSuite harmless from any and all financial losses, including but not limited to: IRS or HMRC tax audits, back-taxes owed due to incorrect S-Corp salary structures, margin calls resulting from SBLOC liquidation thresholds being breached, or capital losses from debt avalanche strategies. You assume 100% of the risk for all financial actions you take.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 5 -->
      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          All design systems, UI components, custom formulas, dynamic charts, scripts, and written guides present on this site are the intellectual property of TaxDebtWealthSuite and are protected by applicable copyright and trademark laws.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
